---

<Base
  breadcrumbJson={breadcrumbJson}
  schemaJson={schemaJson}
  title="Calories Burned Calculator — 40+ Activities | HealthyBMI"
  description="Calculate calories burned walking, running, cycling, swimming and 40+ activities. Enter your weight and duration for an instant MET-based estimate."
  canonical="https://healthybmicheck.com/calories-burned-calculator"
>

<div class="hero">
  <div class="breadcrumb" style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--ink3);margin-bottom:16px;"><a href="/" style="color:var(--ink3);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> › Calories Burned Calculator</div>
  <h1>Calories Burned<br><em>Calculator</em></h1>
  <p>Find out how many calories you burn during exercise and everyday activities — based on your weight, duration, and activity type.</p>
</div>

<div style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--ink3);margin:0 auto 24px;max-width:720px;padding:0 20px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">Reviewed by <strong>Sarah Mitchell, BSc Nutrition</strong> · Last updated: <strong>June 2026</strong></div>

<div class="container">

  <div class="card">
    <!-- Weight input -->
    <div class="unit-toggle">
      <button class="active" onclick="setUnit('metric')">Metric (kg)</button>
      <button onclick="setUnit('imperial')">Imperial (lb)</button>
    </div>

    <div class="input-group" id="kg-wrap">
      <label for="weight-kg">Your Weight</label>
      <div class="input-wrap">
        <input type="number" id="weight-kg" placeholder="70" min="20" max="300">
        <span class="unit-badge">kg</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="input-group" id="lb-wrap" style="display:none">
      <label for="weight-lb">Your Weight</label>
      <div class="input-wrap">
        <input type="number" id="weight-lb" placeholder="154" min="44" max="660">
        <span class="unit-badge">lb</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="input-group">
      <label for="duration-min">Duration</label>
      <div class="input-row">
        <div class="input-wrap">
          <input type="number" id="duration-min" placeholder="30" min="1" max="600">
          <span class="unit-badge">min</span>
        </div>
